The paper deals with the specification and implementation of systems, which falls under the category of computer science theory (cs.THEORY). The use of automata and logic suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also deals with the specification of systems, which may suggest the sub-category of programming languages (cs.PL). The use of automata and logic also suggests the sub-category of formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL). The paper also deals with the modeling of systems, which may suggest the sub-category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with the implementation of systems, which may suggest the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SE).
